  +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+
  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                        ・
                        ・
  +--+
  |  | = 1dot
  +--+










